Actions.Text: REFERENCE CHANGED TO WAYS AND MEANS

Title: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to Maintenance Supervisor Stephen C. Ebling
Summary: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system in the town of Eden, county of Erie, to Maintenance Supervisor Stephen C. Ebling.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to dedicating a portion of the state highway system to Maintenance Supervisor Stephen C. Ebling
